  "detailed_description": "Echoes of the Abyss is a rogue-lite action game, where world changes based on your Sanity. Eat smaller creatures to gain XP and become bigger, while keeping your Sanity-meter in check.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/c118e352c61c78c9547d17c13a66a1d0.poster.avif?t=1750942372\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/c118e352c61c78c9547d17c13a66a1d0.webm?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/c118e352c61c78c9547d17c13a66a1d0.mp4?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/8a53332919efde05c81a029ee579afaf.poster.avif?t=1750942372\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/8a53332919efde05c81a029ee579afaf.webm?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/8a53332919efde05c81a029ee579afaf.mp4?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Transform XP into stats upgrades OR power-up your 3 base abilities - Shield, Dash and Scream. Find power-runes and imbue your abilities with Poison, Frost, Electricity, Melting Plasma, Push and Vortex. Strategize and create combo synergies. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/40656516eba6f3b262782bd00b2ebf1e.poster.avif?t=1750942372\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/40656516eba6f3b262782bd00b2ebf1e.webm?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/40656516eba6f3b262782bd00b2ebf1e.mp4?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/8995a4e7fc37770af144b553d6d32b5d.poster.avif?t=1750942372\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/8995a4e7fc37770af144b553d6d32b5d.webm?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818080/extras/8995a4e7fc37770af144b553d6d32b5d.mp4?t=1750942372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Survive hordes of creatures ascending from the Abyss and uncover secrets of your lost humanity.",
